467
00:55:59,190 --> 00:56:03,435
Banks turned a blind eye behind the red lines, and it wasn't about the money.

468
00:56:04,616 --> 00:56:07,839
Class was an irresistible force.

469
00:56:07,940 --> 00:56:09,962
Race was an immovable object.

470
00:56:11,820 --> 00:56:28,814
Perhaps it wasn't the written rule, but white folks knew the legal tool to keep us in our place in this mystic valley space, where slaves and rum and ships had built some mansions, made some millionaires, and hid some old money.

471
00:56:30,535 --> 00:56:40,263
So it was hard by the mystic we went, muddy and a bit turned down, the only place where one could be brown in this ancient Middlesex County town.

472
00:56:42,186 --> 00:56:46,827
But we named it, we claimed it, we made it our own.

473
00:56:48,747 --> 00:56:57,089
