474
00:56:59,690 --> 00:57:02,711
We followed its flow to the lakes and the sandy beachfront.

475
00:57:04,091 --> 00:57:08,432
On our own Jordan shore, we baptized and blessed our brothers and sisters in Christ.

476
00:57:09,378 --> 00:57:17,981
We caught the little fishes to go with our loaves of bread and became the teeming multitude who our Lord Jesus fed, hired by the mystic.

477
00:57:21,803 --> 00:57:24,404
We became community.

478
00:57:24,424 --> 00:57:25,825
We commanded unity.

479
00:57:27,525 --> 00:57:31,627
We embraced the village and raised up our children in the way they should go.

480
00:57:37,902 --> 00:57:42,965
As the river ebbs and flows, the tides will turn and our fortune grows.

481
00:57:43,385 --> 00:57:45,286
A few more streets become our home.

482
00:57:45,626 --> 00:57:48,387
Houses on Sharon join Kin on Jerome.

483
00:57:50,488 --> 00:57:55,250
From Duggar Park to the railroad tracks, the white folks make more room for blacks.

484
00:57:55,711 --> 00:57:57,712
